        Parameters:
        mappingName - the name of the mapping
        type - the type of the identifiable element
        identifiableElementName - the name of the identifiable element
        testCode - the mapped test code
        requiredMappings - the required mappings for this mapping
        parameters - the names of object mappings that are used to be method parameters
        callers - the names of object mappings that are used to call methods
        returnObjects - the names of object mappings that are returned by methods
